name: Anupam Roy
text:
So we tried to come up with our anti-virus ‚ÄúBhalo Theko 19‚Äù. The song is set to 19 beats. Hopefully this will cheer you up and give you strength to fight. This could be the cure!
Video premieres on YT on 20th at 5:00pm IST. Do not forget to subscribe to my channel. #BhaloTheko19
location: Place(_api=<tweepy.api.API object at 0x000002189A9232B0>, id='70957ac3123b3249', url='https://api.twitter.com/1.1/geo/id/70957ac3123b3249.json', place_type='city', name='Kolkata', full_name='Kolkata, India', country_code='IN', country='India', contained_within=[], bounding_box=BoundingBox(_api=<tweepy.api.API object at 0x000002189A9232B0>, type='Polygon', coordinates=[[[88.094457, 22.269493], [88.610027, 22.269493], [88.610027, 22.955918], [88.094457, 22.955918]]]), attributes={})

name: Anupam Roy
text: We, musicians have not been able to perform in public for the past 6 months. Locked up in our houses, hearing the word ‚ÄúCOVID-19‚Äù almost 19 times a day made me wonder - what is this 19? How can I translate this 19 into our music? Why don‚Äôt we try and discover our own vaccine?
location: Place(_api=<tweepy.api.API object at 0x000002189A9232B0>, id='70957ac3123b3249', url='https://api.twitter.com/1.1/geo/id/70957ac3123b3249.json', place_type='city', name='Kolkata', full_name='Kolkata, India', country_code='IN', country='India', contained_within=[], bounding_box=BoundingBox(_api=<tweepy.api.API object at 0x000002189A9232B0>, type='Polygon', coordinates=[[[88.094457, 22.269493], [88.610027, 22.269493], [88.610027, 22.955918], [88.094457, 22.955918]]]), attributes={})

name: Anupam Roy
text: COVID-19. A word that has destroyed 2020. Loss of lives, social distancing and economic breakdown, among other things, have almost stopped the earth from spinning. In this gloomy and scary period of our civilisation, countries are trying their best to get the vaccine out.

name: Anupam Roy
text: As artists we dont have pension schemes. We may not even be able to get on the stage tomorrow to perform. But I know every time someone, somewhere sings or plays a ‚ÄúJourney Song‚Äù or a ‚ÄúAmake Amar Moto‚Äù, my royalty share is being collected by IPRS. They will take care of me.
location: Place(_api=<tweepy.api.API object at 0x000002189A9232B0>, id='70957ac3123b3249', url='https://api.twitter.com/1.1/geo/id/70957ac3123b3249.json', place_type='city', name='Kolkata', full_name='Kolkata, India', country_code='IN', country='India', contained_within=[], bounding_box=BoundingBox(_api=<tweepy.api.API object at 0x000002189A9232B0>, type='Polygon', coordinates=[[[88.094457, 22.269493], [88.610027, 22.269493], [88.610027, 22.955918], [88.094457, 22.955918]]]), attributes={})

name: Anupam Roy
text: In situations like these when the music and film industry of the country are at a standstill, we have regularly received substantial royalty cheques from @IPRSmusic . We are grateful to @Javedakhtarjadu for changing the face of this royalty distribution body. (contd)
location: Place(_api=<tweepy.api.API object at 0x000002189A9232B0>, id='70957ac3123b3249', url='https://api.twitter.com/1.1/geo/id/70957ac3123b3249.json', place_type='city', name='Kolkata', full_name='Kolkata, India', country_code='IN', country='India', contained_within=[], bounding_box=BoundingBox(_api=<tweepy.api.API object at 0x000002189A9232B0>, type='Polygon', coordinates=[[[88.094457, 22.269493], [88.610027, 22.269493], [88.610027, 22.955918], [88.094457, 22.955918]]]), attributes={})

name: Anupam Roy
text: Composers and lyricists all over the world are entitled to receive royalties for their  published work throughout their lives. India is no exception. I am glad to be a member of the royalty distribution body of our country, IPRS as a writer-composer. (contd)
